---
title: Pumpkin, Turnip & Veggie Freekeh Salad With Honey Dressing, Herby Mayo & Goat Cheese
description: Let’s get freekeh (pronounced free-kuh)! Sorry. We had to. Freekeh is an ancient grain and nutrition powerhouse often
mentioned alongside superfood heroes like quinoa and farro. With its roasted nuttiness, it's our new favourite base for a
nourishing bowl of big flavours. You’re gonna love it.
